                <note rend="inline" type="source">033.1161/8–1544: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Harriman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-22T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 22, 1944—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2004. Reurtel 3001, August 15, 9 p.m. The President has personally requested that
                    you take up again with Molotov the question of General Fleming’s visit. In your
                    conversation with Molotov you are authorized to express the personal interest of
                    the President in this case.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
